---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import profilePicture from "../assets/images/profilePicture.png";
---

<section id="section2">
  <Image src={profilePicture} alt="Profile picture of Marie Wulff" />
  <article>
    <h4>02/</h4>
    <h2>about</h2>
    <p>
      I’m currently studying at Copenhagen School of Design and Technology. I’ve
      chosen to specialise in <span>frontend</span> design.
    </p>
  </article>
  <div>
    <p>
      I’m would love to study backend developing, and become a full-stack
      developer in the future.
    </p>
    <p>
      In my spare time, catch me hanging out with my friends, working out in my
      local gym or watching a movie in the cinema.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @layer components {
    section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      place-items: center;

      div {
        display: flex;
        background: var(--color-card-bg);
        place-content: space-between;

        p {
          padding: 2rem;
          border-radius: 1rem;
        }
      }
    }

    img {
      width: 320px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 5%;
    }
  }
</style>
